                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a10">
                                    <locus from="177v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title ref="LIT3065RepCh345" type="incomplete"/>, the end is missing. The following is the incipit:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">እሴብሕ፡ ጸጋኪ፡ ኦዑጽፍተ፡ ልብሰ፡ ወርቅ፡ ንግስትየ፡ ወለተ፡ ዳዊት፡ ንጉሥ።</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a11">
